<item>
            <title>[CXF-5626] MessageContext is lost when JAX-WS client is invoked from within a JAX-WS endpoint impl</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CXF-5626</link>
                <project id="12310511" key="CXF">CXF</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When a JAX-WS client is invoked inside an endpoint, the endpoint&apos;s &lt;tt&gt;MessageContext&lt;/tt&gt; is bumped out of the &lt;tt&gt;ThreadLocal&lt;/tt&gt; and is not replaced at the end of the client call.  This makes the &lt;tt&gt;MessageContext&lt;/tt&gt; unavailable to endpoints after they make any JAX-WS invocation.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12702561">CXF-5626</key>
            <summary>MessageContext is lost when JAX-WS client is invoked from within a JAX-WS endpoint impl</summary>
