                            <comment id="13941444" author="klape" created="Thu, 20 Mar 2014 06:26:02 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Possible patch attached&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13943069" author="asoldano" created="Fri, 21 Mar 2014 14:03:08 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;My gut feeling (still have to verify) is that &lt;b&gt;anywhere&lt;/b&gt; we have try-finally blocks setting an clearing the threadlocal reference to the MessageContext in the WebServiceContext, the clear operation should actually be replaced by a restore of the former MessageContext instance (if any, otherwise null).&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
